    • toHome

      public void toHome(javafx.scene.input.MouseEvent mouseEvent) throws IOException
      Redirects to the home page. This method is called when the user clicks on a specific element (e.g., a button, link) to navigate to the home page. It checks the value of the boolean variable 'temp' to determine if the redirection should occur. If 'temp' is true, it creates an instance of the PageController class and calls the 'changePage' method, passing the 'backHome' button as an argument. After the redirection, it sets the value of 'temp' to false to prevent subsequent redirects.
      参数:
      mouseEvent - the mouse event triggered by the user's click.
      抛出:
      IOException - if an I/O error occurs while redirecting to the home page.
